data.description: Welcome home to the Solera Diamond Valley community by Del Webb. The much-coveted "Hamilton Model" solar home with 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom, casita residence spans a generous 2,112 square feet of living space. The traditional and established greenscape enhance the curb appeal.  Step through the security gate and into the spacious sitting porch with covered entrance, where a sense of security and comfort welcomes you. The casita, complete with French doors, it's own bath and large private suite is the perfect spot to relax and unwind. With a tasteful blend of tile and carpeted flooring throughout, neutral and cheery color theme you'll find the ambiance for comfort and relaxation assured.. The living room features a cozy fireplace and a built-in media niche, adjacent is the office, den or craft room, the choice is yours. With a formal dining area for entertaining, and a spacious kitchen that offers breathtaking views of the mountains and warm glow of the fireplace you find ample cabinet storage, countertop space, island, a pantry, white appliances, breakfast nook and breakfast bar for casual meals.  The convenience continues with a dedicated laundry room, complete with overhead cabinets for easy storage. The primary bedroom is a retreat, of generous size, with an ensuite bath featuring dual sinks, a separate tub, a walk-in shower, and an ample walk-in closet. The second suite with private bath provides comfort and privacy. When it's time to enjoy the outdoors, step onto the large California patio, surrounded by concrete and vinyl fencing for privacy. Here, you'll find your own 3-hole putting green on artificial turf, perfect for honing your golf skills, and an established landscape that adds to the beauty and serenity of this exceptional property. This Solera Diamond Valley home is more than just a house; it's a haven of comfort, luxury, and convenience in one of the most sought-after communities.  The Del Webb community center offers a fitness center, walking/jogging track, library, billiard tables, meeting rooms, concierge, indoor pool and spa, as well as two outdoor pools. Engage in friendly matches on the Bocce ball, tennis, and pickleball courts, completing a comprehensive range of activities for an enriched 55+ living experience.
